text:
2022 - 38th Street (center of view), between Twenty-first Ave. (left) and Twentieth Ave. (right), showing, in the left background, the George Kouwenhoven, John Alsop and Peter Rapelye houses. On the right of the enumerated 2-story structure is the gas tank of the Astoria Light, Heat and Power Company. Photographers vantage point is on Steinway Ave.

About 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
